{"tid":187694,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解都巴士佬都咁仆街 (純文字)","createTime":"2017-04-05T06:37:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T23:40:01.000Z","uid":43697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b480183ebb05c71bcb7727c1f45cb910f8d19b8c","tid":187694,"uid":43697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T06:37:48.000Z","msg":"今日又曬又熱 我就企係側邊搵啲牆擋住個太陽 等自己舒服啲 好啦見到架巴士想埋站 我就行埋去 咁個個位係太子街邊啲巴士站黎 我心諗架巴士就停 我就行埋去 架巴士前面無車塞住 我一行埋去 佢同我踩油走 即刻火都黎埋 一直急步行追架巴士 行到側邊就指撚住佢 屌佢老母呢啲巴士司機死全家 人做司機佢做司機做撚到佢咁樣 食得屎啦 點解可以有人企站邊都可以飛站<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a497f9e8b95e9f37d1d5e1479f2ca326c4c8c6","tid":187694,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:14:12.000Z","msg":"You on9"},{"pid":"1b731fa0a280b1b8784b79cfe7049f277de094e9","tid":187694,"uid":40073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:14:44.000Z","msg":"唔撚識截車？<br />\n你估而家搭地鐵呀站站停<br />\n老撚奉？"},{"pid":"1680ed88cd66d7ee837b33eedea3830ff2dc3e30","tid":187694,"uid":43697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T15:39:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔撚識截車？<br />\n你估而家搭地鐵呀站站停<br />\n老撚奉？</blockquote><br />\n理應都停一停睇下有無人想上啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ecb14ed405ee766593cf9a253b06d3602ea521","tid":187694,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T23:38:15.000Z","msg":"你冇伸手有權唔停"},{"pid":"6df49a7eca67c4bf2966dd05c0106f928f161c4a","tid":187694,"uid":52839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T23:39:12.000Z","msg":"你係咪屌爆佢個閪屌穿佢個閪"},{"pid":"b88c4d1b52c2b7c35becde8e42cbe90ad96ad683","tid":187694,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T23:40:01.000Z","msg":"揮手截車都懶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}